      "span_text": "We thus chose the concentration of CRD-AP at which we saw the greatest difference between binding to Nrt-Wnt-expressing and to untransfected cells and tested all of the combinations at this concentration in triplicate. reported that the binding of DFz2CRD-AP to Nrt-Wg-expressing cells was 10-fold higher than to untransfected cells."
